Module biblioteka
Package biblioteka.gui

Class LibraryRepository

java.lang.Object
biblioteka.gui.LibraryRepository
public class LibraryRepository extends Object
Manages the in-memory data for the library application, including lists of available books, borrowed books, and users. This class acts as a central repository for application data, providing ObservableList instances to allow UI components to react to data changes. It also delegates data persistence (saving and loading) to the PersistenceManager. All data modification methods ensure operations are run on the JavaFX Application Thread.
